# {{projectName}}

An academic site built with [Uniweb](https://github.com/uniweb/uniweb) — a component web platform that separates content from code. Designed for researchers, labs, and academic departments.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
pnpm install

# Start development server
pnpm dev

# Build for production
pnpm build
```

